    "description": {
      "zh": "跳蚤市场: 2,700₽ | 物品价值: 2,700 | Mechanic报价: 1,512₽购买渠道 @ Peacekeeper 等级4 < 24$ ≈ 2,898₽\n\n.50 BMG（12.7x99 毫米勃朗宁机枪弹）M33 铅芯普通弹，美国制造。该款弹药于 1923 年正式列装，是 M2 勃朗宁重机枪对付轻装甲载具以及压制轻型掩体后方敌方人员的主力弹种。M33 的停止作用相当惊人，一旦命中目标能够造成巨量伤害。",
      "en": "跳蚤市场: 2,700₽ | 物品价值: 2,700 | Mechanic报价: 1,512₽购买渠道 @ Peacekeeper 等级4 < 24$ ≈ 2,898₽\n\nA .50 BMG (12.7x99mm NATO) M33 Ball cartridge, developed in the USA and adopted in 1923 for Browning M2 machine guns, primarily designed to destroy light armored vehicles and neutralize enemy personnel behind light cover. The cartridge has significant stopping power and is capable of inflicting devastating damage to the target upon impact."
    },
